reviewText: I absolutely loved it. I am glad I am not a movie critic so I can enjoy the movie. it's really nice to watch the makings of the movies too. I just wish there was more of these movies in a series.
I remember seeing this movie in the theater. One of my favorites, so I had to buy it in BluRay.
I enjoyed it greatly, I have forgoting how good it was. Haven't seen it in years and still enjoy it.
